                            <h4>Why do I need to register my car?</h4>
                            <p>
                                In case you plan to be just a passenger who is using the application just for looking for rides and not for creating them, there is no need
                                for you to register your car. In the other case, when you also want to be the one who is driving the other people to the destinations, to create
                                the ride offers there is a need to have a car registered in your profile. Without it, it will not allow you to create a ride because no plate number will
                                be available in the list which is required field in the form.
                            </p>

                            <h4>What is needed for registering my car?</h4>
                            <p>
                                To register a car, you need to be logged in or register. Except for this step, in the registration form are fields like brand, model, number of seats and number plate which are necessary to fill.
                                To get to the Registration form, check please the following How to register a car question.
                            </p>

                            <h4>How to register a car?</h4>
                            <p>
                                Before registering your car, you need to be at first logged in or create a new profile. The first way how to register a car is to check the
                                checkbox with "I want to register a car" statement while registering. This way it will automatically move you to the form for car registration after you save the registration form for a user.
                                Here you can fill all the information and click on Create button. The car will immediately appear in your list of cars.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                The other way when you are just logged in as a user, you need to open your personal profile page by clicking on your name up on the right side.
                                On this page you can see My cars option in which there is a button for creating a new car. After clicking on the button, you are in the registration form for cars. In case you decide not to create the car, you can click on Back to MyCars link under the registration form.
                                As soon as you save all the information, the car is created and shown in your list of cars. The necessary information  For creating a car are Brand,
                                Model, Number of seats and number plate.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                In case you are still completely lost and have no idea how to access the registration form, here is the link but don't forget to be logged in!<br />
                                <a asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Manage/CreateCar">Create a car</a>
                            </p>

                            <h4>Where can I see my registered cars?</h4>
                            <p>
                                You have to be logged in and have at least one car created. Just open your personal profile page by clicking on
                                your name up on the right side. On this page you can see My cars option on the left side in which the list of cars registered by you is shown.
                            </p>

                            <h4>How to edit a car?</h4>
                            <p>
                                You have to be logged in and have the car created to edit it. To do so, you need to open your personal profile page by clicking on
                                your name up on the right side. On this page you can see My cars option on the left side in which the list of cars registered by you is shown. On the right side of each car in
                                the end of the line is the option for Editing the car. After clicking on the blue button with pen the page for editing is opened. Be careful to choose the right car you want to edit. To make sure
                                you chose the right one, all the information are displayed on this Edit Page. If you find out you do not want to edit exactly this one car, you can easily click on the Back
                                to My Cars link in the end of the editing form and choose the right car. If you are sure you want to edit exactly this one car, write the new information where it is needed and click on the Save button in the end
                                of the form. After this action the list of your cars is displayed again with all the new information.
                            </p>

                            <h4>How to delete a car?</h4>
                            <p>
                                You have to be logged in and have the car created to delete it. To do so, you need to open your personal profile page by clicking on
                                your name up on the right side. On this page you can see My cars option on the left side in which the list of cars registered by you is shown. On the right side of each car in
                                the end of the line is the option for Deleting the car. After clicking on the red button with trash can the page for deleting is open. Be careful to choose the right car you want to delete. To make sure
                                you chose the right one, all the information are displayed on this Delete Page. If you find out you do not want to delete exactly this one car, you can easily click on the Back
                                to My Cars link in the end and choose the right car. If you are sure you want to delete exactly this one car, click on the red Delete button. After
                                this action, the list of your cars is displayed again, but the car is not shown anymore as well as all its possibilities for creating a ride with this car are not available anymore.
                                After you delete a car, also all bookings and rides connected to this car are deleted.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <b>!!! With car are deleted also all rides and bookings connected to it. !!!</b>
                            </p>
