                            <h4>What does it mean to make a booking?</h4>
                            <p>
                                If you want to join a ride with someone from one place to the other on exact date, you can make a booking of his or her ride. After the driver accepts
                                your request, you can drive together to your destination.
                            </p>

                            <h4>How much does it cost to take a ride?</h4>
                            <p>Our application is fully without money. It means you will not be charged anything as well as no one will pay you for anything.</p>

                            <h4>How to make a booking?</h4>
                            <p>
                                You need to be logged in to book a ride. Go to the page with Rides where you can find the specific ride for you. After you have one, click on the
                                Details link in the end of the line where is the ride. You will see the page with all details and the driver. On the right side, there is a button for booking
                                the ride. After you click on it, you will see your list of bookings with the booking statuses. Now you have to wait until the driver accept or reject your request.
                                In case you have already booked the ride the button for booking it will not allow you to book it once again as well as the system will not allow you to book your own ride.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                You can also open your pesonal profile page and choose My bookings option on your left. Here you can see a button Book a Ride which will redirect you to the page with all rides. Here continue as mentioned above.
                            </p>

                            <h4>Where can I see my bookings?</h4>
                            <p>
                                To see your bookings you need to be logged in. Open your personal profile page and choose My bookings section. Here you can see the list of all your bookings with all their statuses.
                            </p>

                            <h4>What do booking statuses mean?</h4>
                            <p>
                                Our system has exactly 4 different booking statuses. Pending means that the driver has not accept or reject your booking. Accepted means that the driver agrees with driving you to the destination. Rejected on the other hand means
                                that the driver does not wish to drive with you. And the last one is cancelled, what means that even if you were accepted, something might have happened and the driver eventually decided to cancel your acceptance or you can also be the one who eventually decides
                                not to take the ride with the driver and cancels the booking.
                            </p>

                            <h4>Is it possible to cancel my booking?</h4>
                            <p>
                                You can always cancel the booking in case you cannot join the ride. You can do so on your own profile page in MyBookings section. There you can find the Cancel button next to the booking you wish to cancel. Make sure you are cancelling the right one.
                            </p>

                            <h4>Is it possible to cancel the booking even after the driver has confirmed it?</h4>
                            <p>You can always cancel the booking if you cannot join the ride. To find more information how to cancel it, check the previous question Is it possible to cancel my booking?</p>

                            <h4>How do I know if my booking has been accepted by the driver?</h4>
                            <p>You can see it under the notification bell or under My bookings on your personal profile page. Each of these pages is showing the status of your bookings.</p>

                            <h4>How to contact a driver who accepted my booking?</h4>
                            <p>
                                To contact the driver, open the detailed page of the ride and there you can see the Area with Send me a message. This message is sent to the driver. To find out more about Message, check the Messages section in questions for everyone using the App.
                            </p>

                            <h4>What is the search function in bookings for?</h4>
                            <p>
                                The search function on pages with bookings is for searching the bookings with the same status. It means, when you want to see all Accepted bookings for example, you can just type Accepted into the search field and you will see all of them.
                                By this way you can for example find out which driver is rejecting you or cancelling your bookings more often than others.
                            </p>
